I was five, without even memorizing them!

00:08:01.708 --> 00:08:03.333
Hello, who wants it?

00:08:03.416 --> 00:08:05.916
Give it to me.
Poetry's not his cup of tea.

00:08:06.208 --> 00:08:07.250
100 euros.

