00:33:38.583 --> 00:33:40.958
I was sent here
on a research mission.

00:33:41.083 --> 00:33:43.333
Boy, what a welcome I got!

00:33:43.416 --> 00:33:45.208
Somebody stole my remote.

00:33:46.333 --> 00:33:49.791
Without it,
I can't signal my people.

00:33:49.958 --> 00:33:53.125
And without a signal
they won't come for me.

00:33:53.666 --> 00:33:56.000
They'll think it's a perilous planet.

00:33:56.250 --> 00:33:57.875
That I'm dead as a dodo.

00:34:04.375 --> 00:34:05.791
Listen.
- What?

00:34:05.958 --> 00:34:07.708
